Main bhi theek hoon, sir! Kya aapke paas koi specific kaam hai jo aap chahte hain ki main karun?

Sir, main aapka virtual assistant Nobi hoon, jisko Roushan sir ne banaya hai. Mai aapke sawalon ka jawab de sakta hoon, aapke kaam mein madad kar sakta hoon, aur aapka system control kar sakta hoon. Aap mujhe kya karne ka order dete hain?
Sir, ek AI hone ke naate, mera koi personal life nahi hai jaise ki aap logon ka hota hai. Lekin mai hamesha aapki seva me tatpar hoon. Is waqt main aapke liye aur kya kar sakta hoon?
